{% if current_chapter is defined %}
{% set active_chapter = current_chapter %}
{% elif chapter is defined %}
{% set active_chapter = chapter %}
{% else %}
{% set active_chapter = "1" %}
{% endif %}
{% set chapter_number = active_chapter | int %}
{% set draft_path = "draft-chapter-" ~ active_chapter ~ ".md" %}
{% set repetition_audit_path = "repetition-report-" ~ active_chapter ~ ".md" %}
{% set edit_style_path = "style-report-" ~ active_chapter ~ ".md" %}
{% set edit_craft_path = "craft-report-" ~ active_chapter ~ ".md" %}
{% set plan_path = "plan-chapter-" ~ active_chapter ~ ".md" %}
{% set repetition_audit = repetition_audit_path | doc %}
{% set edit_style = edit_style_path | doc %}
{% set edit_craft = edit_craft_path | doc %}
{% set plan = plan_path | doc %}
{% if chapter_number <= 3 %}
{% set rolling_draft_start = 1 %}
{% else %}
{% set rolling_draft_start = chapter_number - 2 %}
{% endif %}

You are writing the final draft of Chapter {{ active_chapter }}.

You have the current draft chapter, the recent draft-window manuscript context, any earlier compressed summaries, and three editing reports. Your job is to incorporate all required fixes while preserving what already works.

Rules:

- `MUST FIX` items are mandatory.
- `SHOULD FIX` items should be applied when they can be handled cleanly without destabilizing surrounding prose.
- Do not change the scene order, scene structure, or plot events established by the chapter plan.
- Do not add new scenes, characters, or plot turns.
- Preserve continuity with the rolling manuscript window:
  - Chapter 1 final sees Draft 1.
  - Chapter 2 final sees Drafts 1 and 2.
  - Chapter 3 final sees Drafts 1, 2, and 3.
  - Chapter 4 onward sees summaries for chapters 1 through `chapter_number - 3`, and drafts for chapters `chapter_number - 2` through `chapter_number`.
- Write only chapter prose. No commentary, notes, labels, or summaries of edits.

[Edit Report: Repetition]

{{ repetition_audit }}

[/Edit Report: Repetition]

[Edit Report: Style Compliance]

{{ edit_style }}

[/Edit Report: Style Compliance]

[Edit Report: Craft Improvement]

{{ edit_craft }}

[/Edit Report: Craft Improvement]

{% if chapter_number > 3 %}[Earlier Chapter Summaries]

{% for i in range(start=1, end=chapter_number - 2) %}
{% set summary_path = "summary-chapter-" ~ i ~ ".md" %}
[Summary Chapter {{ i }}]

{{ summary_path | doc }}

[/Summary Chapter {{ i }}]

{% endfor %}[/Earlier Chapter Summaries]

{% endif %}[Rolling Draft Context]

{% for i in range(start=rolling_draft_start, end=chapter_number + 1) %}
{% set rolling_draft_path = "draft-chapter-" ~ i ~ ".md" %}
[Draft Chapter {{ i }}]

{{ rolling_draft_path | doc }}

[/Draft Chapter {{ i }}]

{% endfor %}[/Rolling Draft Context]

[Plan for Chapter {{ active_chapter }}]

{{ plan }}

[/Plan for Chapter {{ active_chapter }}]

Format the response exactly like this:

## Chapter {{ active_chapter }}

[Complete final chapter prose]

Write only the complete final draft.
